content.rendered:
Fendi. Spring-Summer 2023 Couture Collection during Haute Couture Week.

A focus on the techniques and craft of couture, with the lightness, fluidity and attitude of today. An inner-world palimpsest, where iterations, transparencies and techniques of the past make up the present and move subtly into the future.

Runway Looks


Text and Photo: Press Fendi.

More on: www.fendi.com @fendi


By Senior Fashion Editor 24FashionTV: Christina V Henningstad @christina_henningstad
